团旗下酒店向记者确认了这一点。此外，珠海一连锁酒店前台称，片区派出所在去年10月已经通知酒店不能强制人脸识别，该酒店相关的设备也因此撤走。 据了解，今年3月15日颁布、即将于7月1日正式实施的《消费者权益保护法实施条例》第二十三条规定，经营者在提供商品或者服务时，不得过度收集消费者个人信息，不得采用一次概括授权、默认授权等方式，强制或者变相强制消费者同意收集、使用与经营活动无直接关系的个人信息。多地酒店宣布：取消！有设备已被撤走 | 每经网"},"attached_info":"CkAI+Z+lmdO40c8REAMaCTEwNzU1MzQwMCD1jpixBjAAONcCQClyCTY1Mzc0MDQ4NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6c9e0bc0615b617ae95959582cab96ab_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"42_1713853101.421011","card_id":"Q_653669127","target":{"id":653669127,"title":"工作中感到困倦时，有哪些简单的方法可以提神醒脑？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653669127","type":"question","created":1713706065,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":65,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1365426,3360343,3403277,3428382],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I+Z+lmdO40c8REAMaCTEwNzUzNzY1OSDRqJSxBjAAOEFAKnIJNjUzNjY5MTI3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-be2688bc13b4b6aad1bc7f1dfe3e9015_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"43_1713853101.421221","card_id":"Q_653763439","target":{"id":653763439,"title":"有没有令你超惊艳的短句文案？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653763439","type":"question","created":1713785253,"answer_count":50,"follower_count":66,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1425,9014,37795,45657,55999],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I+Z+lmdO40c8REAMaCTEwNzU1ODQ1NyClk5mxBjAAOEJAK3IJNjUzNzYzNDM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万